    "bug_report_description": "During a combat encounter, an enemy NPC appears suspended horizontally several feet above the street surface, with no ground collision or proper ragdoll animation. This makes the character look clipped into thin air and breaks immersion. It could also lead to unintended targeting or collision detection issues if players attempt to shoot or interact with the stuck NPC.",
