    "bug_report_description": "When the player or companion stands near the edge of this rocky slope, their character model sinks into and intersects the rock surface. The lower body and legs are embedded in the geometry, leaving only the upper torso visible. This clipping glitch breaks visual immersion and could potentially trap the character against the rock, impacting movement and interaction.",
    "affected_item": "Character model (player/companion) collision"
}

