    "bug_report_description": "The aircraft’s wing top faces have failed to load their correct paint or material and are instead rendered with a default checkerboard debug texture. This breaks visual immersion and makes it difficult to verify actual livery or damage on the wings. It may also indicate broader material-loading issues that could affect other aircraft components.",
