  "bug_report_description": "When interacting with the IT-specialist NPC, the character’s head model fails to render, leaving a void/black sphere and clipped neck area. Additionally, the UI nameplate above the NPC displays a plain white rectangle instead of the expected text or portrait. This breaks immersion, makes the NPC unrecognizable, and may confuse players about whom they are speaking with. The issue could stem from a missing mesh asset, LOD streaming failure, or a localization/text fallback problem.",
