    "bug_report_description": "When the soldier goes prone on the concrete dock, the character model sinks into the ground, leaving only the upper body and weapon visible. This suggests the collision bounds for the prone animation are misaligned with the terrain mesh height. The clipping obstructs player visibility of their own character and may interfere with hit detection or immersion.",
