  "bug_report_description": "An arrow prop is incorrectly positioned behind the NPC character. It hovers in mid-air and intersects both the character’s shoulder and the background wall. This distraction breaks immersion and suggests an error in the arrow’s attachment point or collision handling during scene rendering.",
