{
    "reasoning": "The NPC’s character model is displaying large bright cyan areas (likely a debug UV color) through the jacket and missing geometry on the hands, indicating reversed normals, missing polygons or a failed texture/shader assignment. This exposes the interior mesh rather than the intended clothing textures.",
